

REST API with ExpressJS
-------------------------


PM

   REST API
   -----------------------------------
   
   URI - /products
   
   GET /products
   GET /products?start=0&size=10
   GET /products/{id}
   
   
   POST /products
   
   PUT /products/{id}
   
   DELETE /products/{id}
   
   
   data representation ==> JSON
   
   
   ------------------------------------